room_title: Escape room "Abandoned School Room" by Houston Panic Room in Houston
room_description: Albert Weinstein's new artificial intelligence technology can change the world. Whether it will be for the good or for the bad is up to you. He hid the blueprints for the invention in the chemistry classroom at his old school. In an hour, the building is scheduled for demolition. Locate the blueprints and escape before it's too late!
